  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to the wacky world of FuryDough, where the real villains are... wait for it... CRAZY DONUTS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350880/extras/0b94fca6a8272afcc7bc01e6950107ae.poster.avif?t=1734093024\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350880/extras/0b94fca6a8272afcc7bc01e6950107ae.webm?t=1734093024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350880/extras/0b94fca6a8272afcc7bc01e6950107ae.mp4?t=1734093024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into chaotic battles, dodge wild enemies, and unlock quirky abilities like Panic Mode, Almost Hurts, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arm yourself with a ridiculous arsenal, including the Whisk Whipper, Broccoli Machine Gun, and other absurd weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350880/extras/7266bbe14fba70240785373bbdbc00a7.avif?t=1734093024\" width=616 height=362 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive endless roguelite action in a maze of madness where donuts reign supreme. Are you ready for the challenge?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350880/extras/5061c5f15b4319a0145921d6d361400b.poster.avif?t=1734093024\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350880/extras/5061c5f15b4319a0145921d6d361400b.webm?t=1734093024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350880/extras/5061c5f15b4319a0145921d6d361400b.mp4?t=1734093024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BUY NOW</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350880/extras/8e43aeee414d717a044e1e1db4247da6.poster.avif?t=1734093024\" width=616 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350880/extras/8e43aeee414d717a044e1e1db4247da6.webm?t=1734093024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350880/extras/8e43aeee414d717a044e1e1db4247da6.mp4?t=1734093024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
